---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import Link from "../../components/Link.astro";
import profilePicture from "../../images/profile.webp";
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
	pageTitle="Diego Rivero – Data Scientist and Geospatial Engineer"
	pageDescription="I'm Diego, a data scientist and geospatial engineer with lots of experience in GIS data analysis and transformations for BPO and Telecom. Nice to meet you!"
	profilePicture={profilePicture}
	lang="en"
>
	<div>
		<h2 id="about">About me</h2>
		<p>
			I'm Diego, a data scientist and geospatial engineer working in the Telecom and BPO sectors. With 8 years of experience in databases, SQL, and geospatial data management, I lead ELT implementation, data warehousing, and data modeling. Skilled in SQL reporting with SSRS/Power BI. Native Spanish speaker and C2 certified in English. Passionate about all things data, especially geospatial data analysis. Open to new opportunities and collaborations.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div>
		<h2 id="skills">Things I know</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Data transformation (dbt)</li>
			<li>ELT (Extract, Load, Transform)</li>
			<li>Data modeling and database design</li>
			<li>SQL and NoSQL databases (Postgres, SQL Server, SQLite, Redis)</li>
			<li>GIS – Geographic Information Systems (PostGIS, QGIS, ArcGIS)</li>
			<li>Public clouds (AWS, Azure, DigitalOcean)</li>
			<li>Cloud data management platforms (Databricks, Deepnote)</li>
			<li>Programming languages (Python, SQL, C#)</li>
			<li>Docker and containerization</li>
			<li>Pipeline orchestration (Prefect)</li>
			<li>Data warehousing (Redshift)</li>
			<li>Data visualization (Tableau, Power BI)</li>
			<li>Data quality and testing</li>
			<li>Lots of Excel (xlookup/vlookup, tables and pivot tables, embedded SQL queries, VBA)</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<div>
		<h2 id="portfolio">Things I've done</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>
				A fork of a bot to repost memes to Twitter called
				<Link
					link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/tootbot"
					text="Tootbot"
				/>.
			</li>
			<li>
				A WhatsApp bot that adds many simple utilities like transcribing voicenotes or pictures, which you can find
				<Link
				link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/whatsapp-utils/"
				text="here"
				/>.
			</li>
			<li>
				A page to know how close to the 1% top earners would you be in my country called
				<Link
				link="https://geih.drivero.com.co/"
				text="salary-o-meter"
				/>
				(which uses Colombian pesos)
			</li>
			<li>
				An implementation of a Mandelbrot set renderer in F# (my favorite hobby language) that is available
				<Link
				link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/mset/"
				text="on my GitHub"
				/>.
			</li>
			<li>
				A compilation of useful
				<Link
				link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/sql-server-scripts/"
				text="Microsoft SQL Server scripts"
				/>.
			</li>
			<li>
				A page that makes anything you write into a cube in markdown code block format called
				<Link
					link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/shitposting-cube/"
					text="Cubeposter"
				/>.
			</li>
			<li>
				This website, which was built in 
				<Link
				link="https://astro.build/"
				text="Astro"
				/>, and you can find
				<Link
					link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/website-dataeng/"
					text="the source code for it here"
				/>.
			</li>
			<li>
				Check out
				<Link
					link="https://github.com/isthistechsupport/"
					text="my GitHub"
				/>
				to see what other (open source) things I've done!
			</li>
			<li>
				I've also done a lot of closed source work on the technical side of management consulting for the telecom & tech industry, plus a lot of data pipelines and data management (and people management, too) for the BPO industry.
			</li>
			<li>
				If you like what I do enough to want me to do something for you, great! I also do all sorts of technical consulting work as a freelancer
				and I'm pretty sure I can help you out. See <a href="#contact">my contact details below</a>.
			</li>
		</ul>
