		</ul>
	</div>

	<div>
		<h2 id="likes">Things I like (enough to do them in my free time)</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Functional programming</li>
			<li>Reading – a lot of reading</li>
			<li>World History & Geopolitics</li>
			<li>Art, especially painting and classical music</li>
			<li>Music, especially indie and alternative rock</li>
			<li>Traveling</li>
			<li>Landscape photography (I love sunsets)</li>
			<li>Cooking (I especially love mediterranean cuisine, from Spain to Turkey)</li>
			<li>Star Wars (I like the sequels more than the prequels)</li>
			<li>
				<Link
					link="https://mikejacobsen.tumblr.com/post/58177900777/this-is-available-as-a-print-iphone-case-and"
